[Although the clinical signs are suggestive of chronic wasting disease and
not necessarily suggestive of epizootic hemorrhagic disease, it is a bit
unexpected for the diagnosis to be EEE. Lesions of CWD are relatively
distinct on pathology; it also makes one wonder whether there has been any
EEE testing in animals confirmed with CWD. - Mod.TG]
